Enumeration Type Documentation

enum HAL_ResetReason_t

The reset reason types.

Enumerator:
NULL_PTR_DEREF_RESET 

jump to the NULL pointer was issued.

POWER_ON_RESET 

the supply voltage was below reset threshold.

EXTERNAL_RESET 

a low level was present on RESET pin.

BROWN_OUT_RESET 

the supply voltage was below Brown-out reset threshold. Set by fuses.

WDT_RESET 

Watch Dog Timer period expired.

JTAG_RESET 

MCU was reset by JTAG.

WARM_RESET 

software reset.
